author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Raysearch Q4 operating profit down slightly yr/yr​
text:
Feb 15 (Reuters) - Raysearch:
* Q4 ‍OPERATING PROFIT SEK 98.7 M (100.2)​ * Q4 ‍ORDER INTAKE EXCLUDING. SERVICE AGREEMENTS SEK 192.6 M (189.0), OF WHICH RAYSTATION/RAYCARE SEK 183.2 M (176.3)​
* Q4 ‍NET SALES SEK 204.9 M (191.4), OF WHICH REVENUES FROM RAYSTATION/RAYCARE SEK 192.6 M (174.8)​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Stockholm Newsroom)
